---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 131
By: Angelus Silesius
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Suffering Transmuted Into Joy
  - Combat-Action=Judgement=The Fire of Heaven
---
Man, if thou art faithful to God, and desirest nought but Him,
The harshest affliction will be for thee a Paradise.
